      "content": "i know u should talk to a doctor but they aren't even answering my calls right now and i'm just trying to be cautious. if i'm being really careful and only had a few bites of food, wouldnt the risk of a crash be way higher than actually needing the insulin? it feels safer to just skip it tonight than to risk a low, right?",
